Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two people's deductions and suspense\Nfill the gulf between love and hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shining stages of Broadway!{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big case with Ran and my mom!{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After we solved the case in Yokohama's Chinatown, Ran suddenly collapsed.{USO/TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In her delirium, she remembered a case from the past.{TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:02:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was when my mom convinced us to attend a musical in New York.{USO/TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of the theater, Mom's old friend, the famous actress Sharon Vineyard, was waiting.{USO/TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was going to give us a backstage tour, but as we walked through the wings before the show...{TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The costumes for the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're up there so they won't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Ran...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost at the hospital...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You okay, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Someone... someone's after my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so... The rope must have broken since it's so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, who put such an old armor up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it could've been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're lucky that large mirror wasn't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's our guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you two. You shouldn't be thanking a mirror or any god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be thanking{\i1} her{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you! You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, we need to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll see you after the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cut myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, do I have a bandage...{TMS}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it, there's no such thing as God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If God existed, this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going home, Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not staying to watch the play, Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning to, but I've got business elsewhere.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it looks like a storm is rising.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I think I'll pass.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't see shows like {\i1}this{\i0} in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}someone{\i0} doesn't seem to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! At least try to pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so interesting about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All they did was turn a Greek myth into a romantic comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what Greek myth is this based on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Golden Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, there were three goddesses: Hera, Athena and Aphrodite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were invited to a banquet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Eris, who wasn't invited,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,got jealous and sent the three a golden apple with a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"For the Fairest."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the three goddesses decided that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the prince of Troy should choose who should get the apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each of them tried to bribe him with promises if he picked her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the guy we met before is playing the unfortunate prince of Troy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The actress playing the wife of the rich man is Zeus' wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hera, the goddess of matrimony who promised him he'd be the world's most powerful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Japanese-looking actress with a lot of character is Athena,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the goddess of wisdom who promised him victory in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:07:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that sexy actress is the goddess of beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aphrodite, who promised him the world's most beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the one in the last scene with the grim look, who was jealous of the other three
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is the one who gave them the golden apple: Eris, the goddess of strife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this version of the story, the rich lady offers the guy money,{MIYAKI-loose}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the smart lady offers him a great job,{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the babe offers him a date,{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the golden apple has been changed{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to a jeweled apple-shaped necklace.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So who did the prince choose?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aphrodite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to legend, that's how the Trojan War got started.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's the Greek myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This musical is quite different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you see the prince's identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...you're going to be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Behold, sinful humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michael? The archangel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kiddin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carefully listen to my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heath...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me this isn't happening...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right... This must be a joke...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. It's not a joke. It's a murder!{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A handgun...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shot with a handgun?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what it looks like.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should probably evacuate too.{TMS/MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, take care of Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Figured I wouldn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bullet casing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good Lord!{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! Heath Flockheart!{MIYAKI-loose-ltil: "no way, the one who was shot was Heath Flockheart"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know him, Captain?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife's a big fan of his.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's the situation?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've asked the actors to wait in their dressing rooms,{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but most of the audience has fled.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shot straight in the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bullet's lodged into the wings in his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wings in his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the bullet's entry wound, I'd say he was shot from a 40° angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,40°...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty sharp angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the killer was probably up on that terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used a laser sight to aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Night Baroness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be watching the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea the musical would turn into a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shot during the climax where the angel appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that scene, smoke is released,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The actor is lifted while the projection in the mirror slides up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making it look like he's emerging from the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's set up in a way to make it look real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So basically, the killer shot him from that terrace as he was rising from the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, he threw the gun onto the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to cause a panic, and therefore be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But are you sure about this? The killer being in the terrace, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. Thanks to the smoke on-stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could clearly see a red beam of light pointing to the stage from the terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My son saw it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Son?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, he's standing right next to you.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the son you're always talking about, Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, isn't he Yusaku's spitting image?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're just as big pranksters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious person reserved every seat in the terrace a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this person was wearing a scarf and hat, so we don't even know if it was a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that must be the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why pick that seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't those seats expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The angle from that terrace isn't very good, so they're probably cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's easy to leave an impression if someone with their face hidden asks for an entire area,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which is exactly what the killer wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are these two strange marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the neck. Doesn't it look like a burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's blood in his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could the blood be from grabbing his chest after he was shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is that it's smudged, like someone tried to clean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have touched his hand somewhere after it got bloody,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing in his clothes, nor is there anything he could've touched in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, has the Night Baroness solved this mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ehh... Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not ask Yusaku? I bet he'd have some ideas.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Yusaku's locked in a hotel room in LA, working.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shame. A celebrity murdered,{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't have a single lead.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be hearing it from the public, the commish{commissioner} {\i1}and{\i0} my wife...{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe Shin'ichi might be able to solve it?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just a kid, he's never investigated a real murder before.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he solved a case while we were on the plane.{MIYAKI/USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sure after the crook was caught he told you he'd known who it was all along.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He loves to brag...{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he was involved in the investigation from the very start.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lined up all the suspects and told them how it happened with that smug look of his.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Holmes or Poirot.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The killer's one of the four actresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right as this case took place, I ran over to the terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a bullet casing, but it wasn't hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This proves someone planted it in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you saw it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A laser sight's red light coming from the terrace to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't know which it was coming from or which it was aimed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That laser sight was probably aimed not from the terrace, but from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to make us believe the gunshot came from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the masked person purchasing the tickets, and the strange present
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were just a ruse to lead us to suspect someone was threatening the actresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is part of the trick, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where that armor fell before the play started, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look carefully at the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a fishing line tied to a nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And next to it, there's a mark, as if something had been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the fishing line was attached to the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then someone did it intentionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The killer probably had a knife or similar in his shoe, and used it to cut the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bringing down the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:17:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer knew that we, Sharon's friends, would come this way during the guided tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that the killer is one of those who was with us when the armor fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as one of the actresses who was on-stage with Heath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, she could aim the laser sight at the terrace, as well as shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the four goddesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Heath is six foot three.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could any of those women shoot {\i1}down{\i0} at him?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, he was behind that mirror!{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! How, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er... I haven't figured that out yet.{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that true, Lila?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heath and I were dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For about five years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you were dating my boyfriend behind my back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be talking about this in a day like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be the angriest of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since your boyfriend apparently had two others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then... Rose too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were dating him too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently all four had a motive for killing Heath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand that he was involved with all three, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What reason does Everith have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the other three, she doesn't have a photo of him on her mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Heath and Everith were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:19:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sharon told me while we were touring around the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They kept it secret even from the other actresses, in case it might affect their popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why she kept glaring at him when he was flirting with the others...{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But right now, we have to figure out how the killer shot him from that height.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rose was the closest one to the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she was acting as if she'd collapsed from seeing the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everith was sitting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Akane was on her knees as if praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who could shoot from the highest was Lila who was standing and holding her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but unlike the other three, her hands weren't hidden by the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People would've noticed if she'd pulled out a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could Heath have been crouching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those wings were bound to his feet, making it completely impossible for him to crouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin'ichi? Have you thought of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought of something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How tall are you?{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,160 cm.{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, five foot three...{USO}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This pamphlet is about 12 inches tall, or one foot...{USO/MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you put this on your head and stand in front of the mirror for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to prove with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:20:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A crack...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:20:59.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,kizu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A crack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a tiny crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd. This mirror's been with the theater for years, and was their guardian angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they'd supposedly get bad luck if they broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what Sharon said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like they glued it together. Were they {\i1}really{\i0} taking care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this curtain look a bit twisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody ran into it when trying to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Shin'ichi, let's get back. Your mom's going to kill us...{MIYAKI}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did it get stuck in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This flip door isn't used for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:04.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see. I understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:08.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The killer used this stage's tricks to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:15.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bloody murder, committed by someone as crafty as the goddess Eris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From those positions, you four couldn't have shot him from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:23:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who turned off the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the killer made use of something in the stage.{something taken out here}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the killer's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only one person could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: Shin'ichi Kudo's New York Case (Case Closed)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,新一「蘭、次回のヒントなんかすんげぇムカツク・・・(--メ)」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,蘭「野生の勘ってやつ？」
